verses.text_plain: The word of the Lord came again unto me, saying,
verses.verse_html: 1The word of the Lord came again unto me, saying,

verses.text_plain: Son of man, there were two women, the daughters of one mother:

verses.text_plain: And they committed whoredoms in Egypt; they committed whoredoms in their youth: there were their breasts pressed, and there they bruised the teats of their virginity.
verses.verse_html: 3And they committed whoredoms in Egypt; they committed whoredoms in their youth: there were their breasts pressed, and there they bruised the teats of their virginity.

verses.text_plain: And the names of them were Aholah the elder, and Aholibah her sister: and they were mine, and they bare sons and daughters. Thus were their names; Samaria is Aholah, and Jerusalem Aholibah.
